n do like 25 probably maybe more.<br><br>COE doesn't stack with coldain ring, not sure how it stacks with o'keils <p><font size="2" face="Arial"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=21797">Veteran Prodigious</a><br>Assassin<br>Fennin Ro</font><br><img src="http://prod.homepage.dk/pics/1106bs.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukayleigh88.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kayleigh88</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/5/02 12:52:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12902.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://communities.msn.ca/_Secure/0MAAAAAQRZJwobQ10JEgBEVnTf2fwE2ks75hF4L27KUCO9em3zq3LL6!q8Jf7rFgS2dffE3vlh*IEAAAAWBMRAw/kayleigh.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Max Damage Shield</span><hr size=1> Spined Chain Mail will give you Bramblecoat effect, i think should stack with all the ds that you mentioned.<br><br>K<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=elegance>Elegance</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/5/02 1:36:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12902.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Max Damage Shield</span><hr size=1> theres the druid ds...dont know what it stacks with though <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left>